metadata.name: Musical Pundit #1
metadata.description:
My first hand drawn piece "Musical Pundit #1" is now available on @withFND.

This #NFTArt is an integration and blend of arts created by HUMAN and ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE. The character of MUSICAL PUNDIT is hand drawn while the background of this #NFT is created through ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE. 

The Ultra HD 8K background for this art took 17.5 hours to generate. While it took almost 8 days for me to finally complete the character with the advice of a few really well established artists. 

Art size 158.73 x 105.82 cm
File Size 20.2 MB
Dimensions 6000 x 4000 pixels
